---
title: American Pulled Chicken & Bacon Jam Burger with Potato Fries & Mayonnaise
description: We’re pulling out the stops for a pulled chicken burger - see what we did there? Let’s jam out for a bacon jam topping - we did it again - and bam, that’s the creation of one delicious burger, pulled together by you. We’ll leave off with the puns now so you can
go and enjoy.
